"  LEMON CURD:","1 3/4 cups granulated sugar","3/4 cup butter, softened","4  large eggs","3  large egg yolks","1 tablespoon lemon zest","3/4 cup fresh lemon juice","  CAKE LAYERS:","1 3/4 cups granulated sugar","1 cup butter, softened","4  large eggs, separated, at room temperature","1 tablespoon orange zest","3 cups cake flour","2 1/2 teaspoons baking powder","1/4 teaspoon table salt","1 cup fresh orange juice","  Shortening","3  (4-inch) wooden skewers","  LEMON-ORANGE BUTTERCREAM FROSTING:","3 cups powdered sugar, sifted and divided","1/2 cup butter, softened","1 tablespoon orange zest"